 What comet_reaper is (so we tune the right thing)

 Not a neural net — no weights file. It's a deterministic algorithm (the orbit_lite planner) steered by
 a config of ~20 numbers. "Tuning" = searching for better numbers in the gym; no gradients/training
 data/.pt. (The training/*.pt files were the abandoned neural track.) Structure today: separate 2P vs
 4P presets + a normal→endgame phase split; no opening book, no opponent profiling.

